  • Constructor Details

    • Art

      public Art(String artTitle, Integer year)
      Constructs a new ArtPiece with the specified Title and Year. The rest of the fields are optional and can be set using setters.
      Parameters:
      artTitle - The title of the artwork (required)
      year - The year the artwork was created (required)
